## Conventions for the chunk docs

Every chunk doc under [`docs/chunks/`](docs/chunks/) follows the same template:

1. **Goal** — one paragraph stating what this chunk accomplishes
2. **Scope: in / out** — explicit boundary so it doesn't drift
3. **Dependencies** — which prior chunks must be done
4. **Files to create or modify** — paths
5. **Detailed tasks** — numbered steps an implementer can follow
6. **Design references** — pointers into any reference materials with line numbers
7. **LLM prompt(s)** — system + user template, output shape, schema (if applicable)
8. **Verification** — how to test the chunk end-to-end
9. **Open questions** — what's still uncertain
